name: Pepeccolo and Rabbs
description:
Inspired by the character piccolo in dragon ball. When I was a kid, I really liked the Dragon Ball Cartoon that was shown on TV every Sunday. One of my favorite characters is Piccolo. Piccolo reminded me of the point that one can be both bad and good in life. I try to combine the characters of Piccolo, Pepe, and Rabbs into one that represents the part of my life.
